{"text_id":78099,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Treat"," Heart"," Disease","\n\n","##"," Work"," with"," a"," doctor"," to"," develop"," a"," treatment"," plan","\n","The"," first"," crucial"," step"," in"," treating"," heart"," disease"," is"," collaborating"," with"," a"," healthcare"," professional"," to"," create"," a"," tailored"," treatment"," plan","."," A"," doctor"," can"," address"," the"," specifics"," of"," your"," condition"," and"," suggest"," the"," most"," appropriate"," interventions","."," This"," may"," include"," lifestyle"," changes",","," medication",","," surgeries",","," or"," a"," combination"," of"," these"," options","."," Keep"," an"," open"," line"," of"," communication"," with"," your"," doctor",","," attend"," all"," recommended"," appointments",","," and"," follow"," the"," prescribed"," routine"," diligently"," to"," manage"," your"," heart"," condition"," effectively",".","\n\n","##"," Consider"," medication","\n","Med","ications"," can"," be"," incredibly"," effective"," in"," managing"," heart"," disease","."," Common"," medications"," include"," those"," that"," lower"," blood"," pressure",","," reduce"," cholesterol"," levels",","," and"," prevent"," blood"," clots","."," Always"," take"," medicines"," precisely"," as"," prescribed",","," and"," be"," aware"," of"," any"," potential"," side"," effects","."," It","\u2019","s"," crucial"," to"," have"," regularly"," scheduled"," follow","-","ups"," with"," your"," physician"," to"," monitor"," the"," effectiveness"," and"," make"," any"," necessary"," adjustments"," to"," the"," dosage"," or"," medication"," type",".","\n\n","##"," Get"," a"," pacemaker"," if"," necessary","\n","A"," pacemaker"," is"," a"," small"," device"," implanted"," in"," the"," chest"," to"," help"," control"," abnormal"," heart"," rhythms","."," If"," your"," doctor"," determines"," that"," your"," heart","\u2019","s"," electrical"," system"," is"," not"," functioning"," properly",","," they"," may"," sugges